    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_12_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_12",
      "description": "Offered here is a truly exceptional specimen that redefines the standard for 'mint' condition. This vehicle has been fastidiously maintained in a climate-controlled environment, showing no signs of the typical wear associated with its age. The exterior paint retains a deep, mirror-like luster, completely free from stone chips, swirl marks, or surface blemishes. Inside, the cabin remains in showroom state; the premium leather upholstery is supple and matte, lacking any bolster wear or creasing, and still carries that distinct new-car aroma. Every electronic component, from the high-fidelity sound system to the advanced driver aids, functions precisely as engineered. Mechanically, it is beyond reproach, with a comprehensive service history documented exclusively through authorized dealerships and all preventative maintenance performed ahead of schedule. This is not just a pre-owned vehicle; it is a preserved piece of automotive excellence for the collector or enthusiast who demands nothing less than perfection.",
      "price": 48500.0,
