      "description": "Hey everyone! I\u2019m honestly so sad to let this beauty go, but it\u2019s time for a new home. This car is in absolutely incredible shape\u2014honestly, it looks and feels like it just rolled off the showroom floor! It's been pampered since day one, kept in a garage, and treated like a member of the family. If you're looking for something that\u2019s basically flawless and ready for a road trip tomorrow, this is the one. Come take a look, you won't be disappointed!",
      "price": 44500.0,
