    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_10_listing_7",
      "firm_id": "sybil_10",
      "description": "Available is an investment-grade 2002 BMW M3 (E46) in concours-ready condition. This example features the iconic S54 3.2L inline-six engine, characterized by its high-compression ratio and six individual throttle bodies that provide instantaneous throttle response up to an 8,000 RPM redline. The Getrag 6-speed manual gearbox offers precise gate engagement, paired with a factory-spec limited-slip differential for optimal torque distribution. This vehicle has undergone comprehensive preventative maintenance, including dual-VANOS servicing and structural subframe reinforcement. The chassis remains exceptionally rigid, supported by a suspension system that retains its original damping characteristics and bushing integrity. With flawless paint depth and a pristine interior, this M3 represents the pinnacle of analog M-division engineering.",
